challenges.description:
Gradient transitions often gradually change from one color to another. When a more abrupt change is required, the transition can be made with a hard stop like this:

```css
linear-gradient(
  var(--first-color) 0%,
  var(--first-color) 40%,
  var(--second-color) 40%,
  var(--second-color) 80%
);
```

